===Definitions===
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# to [[seek]]; to [[look for]]
#: {{zh-x|求《^月亮 ^代表 ^我 的 ^心》的 歌詞|'''looking for''' the lyrics to "The Moon Represents My Heart"}}
#* {{zh-x|嚶 其 鳴 矣，求 其 友 聲。|While ying goes its cry, '''seeking''' with its voice its companion.|ref=Shijing}}
#* {{zh-x|以 若 所 為{wéi} 求 若 所 欲，猶 緣 木 而 求 魚 也。|But doing what you do to '''seek''' for what you desire is like climbing a tree to '''seek''' for fish.|ref=Mencius}}
# to [[beg]]; to [[request]]; to [[implore]]
#: {{zh-x|求 他 別 走|'''begged''' for him to not leave}}
# to [[request]]; to [[ask for]]
# to [[require]]; to [[demand]]
# to [[covet]]; to [[seek]] (fame, riches)
#* {{zh-x|不 忮 不 求，何 用 不臧。|He hates none; he '''covets''' nothing; -What does he which is not good?|ref=Shijing}}
# to [[attract]]
# {{surname|zh}}

